---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section class="py-10">
  <SectionHeading id="about" title="About" />
  <div class="prose-slate space-y-4 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
    <p>
      I started at InnoGames in 2013 as a game developer, working on browser and mobile games used
      by millions of players. Over the years I moved into engineering leadership, then product, and
      I'm now a Senior Product Manager leading multidisciplinary teams shipping mobile games and
      owning product P&L.
    </p>
    <p>
      What I care about now: AI as practical tooling, building small things that matter, and
      bringing engineering rigor into product decisions. On the side I keep a steady stream of
      experiments going. They are how I learn fastest.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside work I'm an Ironman finisher and amateur triathlete. Endurance is the closest analogy
      I've found to product work: long races, slow compounding, treat each kilometer like it
      matters. I treat product the same way. Not a sprint.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
